nodes.bodyText: I prefer the _CONFIG at the end, as this isn't a stronghold but a stronghold config

@Kroppeb no, this class is already a config holder, and the actual instance field that holds the stronghold config you've already named stronghold below. You need consistency here. Should you add config suffix for this field, you should do so for the other 3 fields ((default)structure/stronghold) and apparently config suffix is unnecessary as this class is already StructuresConfig
